"Breathe life" üå∏ explores the concept of human as a creator of life. I asked AI to imagine a person as a god/goddess with a body made of flowers. The results are unexpectedly graceful and beautiful in how the machine sees the creator.

This collection is a reminder to breathe and keep going no matter how hard it is to find happiness again after a time of hardship. Remember to blossom from within and stay inspired to create a limitless universe full of love and positive experiences.
